{"word":"G3927 - παρεπίδημος - parepídēmos - par-ep-id'-ay-mos - Pilgrim","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">παρεπίδημος</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">parepídēmos</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">par-ep-id'-ay-mos</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Pilgrim</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"பரதேசிகளான, சிதறியிருக்கிற - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"stranger; sojourning in a strange place, a foreigner"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G3844 - παρά - pará - par-ah'/3844\">G3844</a> and the base of <a href=\"#/G1927 - ἐπιδημέω - epidēméō - ep-ee-day-meh'-o/1927\">G1927</a>; an <i>alien alongside</i>, that is, a <i>resident foreigner:</i> - pilgrim, stranger.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G1218/1218\">G1218</a>, <a href=\"#/G1553/1553\">G1553</a>, <a href=\"#/G1736/1736\">G1736</a>, <a href=\"#/G3927/3927\">G3927</a>"}]}